{"tid":2459314,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU 終於要上音樂節目打歌啦！已敲定無線三台行程","createTime":"2021-03-24T05:48:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T08:06:43.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"abe5314b8fb6dfaf79c2636f7d0ac51ed61637e9","tid":2459314,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T05:48:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_7049c87ece378b709c76a7d3ae1de550/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-24/134445-901018.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_7049c87ece378b709c76a7d3ae1de550%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-24%2F134445-901018.png&h=4772101d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIU 最近接連有兩支影片破億，在這同時，她也確定會上打歌節目宣傳新專輯〈LILAC〉！<br />\n<br />\nIU 明天（25 日）就會正式發行第五張正規專輯〈LILAC〉，而 EDAM Entertainment 今天除了公開同名主打歌的 MV 預告片，也透露她會從 27 日開始 MBC 和 SBS 和 KSB 的打歌節目外，且安排了各式各樣的綜藝節目行程。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zZsgcVxuYU4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzZsgcVxuYU4&d=bXICEjaVmsGxuRkiXhyD2P1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=04b17c67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zZsgcVxuYU4</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_9ad3e02f347c847cf7132260dc374293/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-24/134445-901019.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_9ad3e02f347c847cf7132260dc374293%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-24%2F134445-901019.jpg&h=a1a394c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一方面，IU 於 2018 年 10 月公開的十週年特別單曲 &ldquo;BBIBBI&rdquo;，官方 MV 在昨天突破兩億大關。這支 MV 有著設定了多種超現實的夢幻場景，搭配一針見血的歌詞，在公開後不到一年就成為她出道後最快破億的 MV。<br />\n<br />\n緊接著，IU 的〈Love poem〉主打歌 &ldquo;Blueming&rdquo; MV 也在今天破億，成為 IU 的第四支破億 MV，也為這次回歸帶來好預兆！<br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：EDAM Entertainment）"},{"pid":"a123b0b320454234d976d8d6e1c3c5af8f10d2dc","tid":2459314,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T05:48:58.000Z","msg":"巧巧天<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab456151ff7a670a157155bd1645c706582a4f3","tid":2459314,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T05:50:17.000Z","msg":"好靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb8bbd7773c44039426d43de0ba175f7522471b","tid":2459314,"uid":339805,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T05:51:52.000Z","msg":"點解可以有咁完美既女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d64bcad1d717a558f0333b8863e22d9aa6c5d14","tid":2459314,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cb8bbd7773c44039426d43de0ba175f7522471b","tid":2459314,"uid":339805,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T05:51:52.000Z","msg":"點解可以有咁完美既女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T05:53:27.000Z","msg":"未至於完美<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2390e33380d995757008cd0231397a5979bcf805","tid":2459314,"uid":308570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T06:02:51.000Z","msg":"戀愛了<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af93ea3591a3d2d461106c4be84cf863e4d0f7c3","tid":2459314,"uid":8612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T08:06:43.000Z","msg":"俾bg嚇到出山打歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}